tions, regulatory hurdles, and real-world variability—positioning the finding as a step forward, not a breakthrough.","keyPoints":["Dva nova proteina poboljšavaju točnost detekcije raka gušterače","Četveromarkerni test prepoznaje bolest u 90% slučajeva","Rana dijagnoza ključna — ali test još nije u kliničkoj primjeni"],"source":{"name":"ScienceDaily Health","url":"https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2026/03/260323005540.htm"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/pancreatic-cancer-blood-test-real-progress-with-re/main.jpg","alt":"Krvi u tragovima: novi test otkriva rak gušterače rano"},"subtitle":"Razina dokaza: istraživački stadij s jasnim ograničenjima","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/pancreatic-cancer-blood-test-real-progress-with-re/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Razina dokaza: istraživački stadij s jasnim ograničenjima"},"tags":["Pancreatic Cancer","Early Detection","Clinical Trial"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$7","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-a-brainstem-link-to-hypertensionwhat-the-evidence-","title":"Mozak i hipertenzija: neočekivano otkriće u moždanom deblu","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Visoki krvni tlak, koji pogađa gotovo trećinu odrasle populacije u Hrvatskoj, dugo se smatrao uglavnom problemom srca, krvnih žila i bubrega.","execSummary":"This study identifies a brainstem region linking breathing control to blood pressure regulation, offering a new mechanistic insight into hypertension—but remains far from clinical application. The angle focuses on separating proven findings (neural pathway) from unanswered questions (therapeutic potential, safety, human trials).","keyPoints":["Regija u moždanom deblu povezuje disanje i krvni tlak","Isključivanje zone snižava tlak u eksperimentima","Za pacijente još uvijek nema izravne terapije"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/a-brainstem-link-to-hypertensionwhat-the-evidence-/main.jpg","alt":"Mozak i hipertenzija: neočekivano otkriće u moždanom deblu"},"subtitle":"Što studija stvarno pokazuje – i što još uvijek ne znamo","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/a-brainstem-link-to-hypertensionwhat-the-evidence-/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što studija stvarno pokazuje – i što još uvijek ne znamo"},"tags":["Hypertension","Brain Research","Neurology"],"geo":{"name":"Hrvatska (Croatia)","lat":45.1,"lon":15.2,"countryCode":"HR"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$8","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-exercise-may-rewire-brains-scarred-by-childhood-tr","title":"Fizička aktivnost preslikava mozak nakon djetinjstva u traumi","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Dugogodišnje uvjerenje da djetinjstvo obilježeno traumom ostavlja trajne neurološke ožiljke dobilo je novu nijansu.","execSummary":"This study shifts the narrative from 'permanent damage' to 'modifiable resilience' in trauma-affected brains, but its observational nature means no direct clinical application yet. The key tension lies between promising neuroplasticity signals and the lack of actionable protocols—highlighting what’s possible, not what’s proven.","keyPoints":["Vježbanje pojačava unutarnju komunikaciju mozga nakon traume","Studija otkriva: trauma nije trajna neurološka presuda","Što ovo znači za pacijente danas – i što još ne znamo"],"source":{"name":"MedicalXpress","url":"https://medicalxpress.com/news/2026-03-physical-reshapes-neural-brain-resilient.html"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/exercise-may-rewire-brains-scarred-by-childhood-tr/main.jpg","alt":"Fizička aktivnost preslikava mozak nakon djetinjstva u traumi"},"subtitle":"Nove spoznaje o neuroplastičnosti: koliko je mozak promjenjiv?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/exercise-may-rewire-brains-scarred-by-childhood-tr/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Nove spoznaje o neuroplastičnosti: koliko je mozak promjenjiv?"},"tags":["Neuroplasticity","Childhood Trauma","Brain Development"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$9","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-gut-bacteria-and-diet-a-10-000-person-study-with-l","title":"Hrana, mikrobiom i zdravlje: što nam 10.000 ljudi otkriva","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada je riječ o prehrani, sve je individualno.","execSummary":"This large-scale observational study (10,068 participants) maps persistent food-microbiome links, suggesting potential for personalized nutrition—but remains at the research stage. The angle focuses on what the evidence *actually* shows (correlations, not causation) and why patients shouldn’t expect clinical changes yet, while highlighting the study’s methodological limits and next steps for validation.","keyPoints":["Jasne veze između prehrane i crijevnih bakterija","Podaci s 10.068 sudionika – ali još uvijek istraživački stadij","Moguća prilagođena prehrana za bolje srčano zdravlje"],"source":{"name":"Nature Medicine","url":"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-026-04312-x"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/gut-bacteria-and-diet-a-10-000-person-study-with-l/main.jpg","alt":"Hrana, mikrobiom i zdravlje: što nam 10.000 ljudi otkriva"},"subtitle":"Velika studija pokazuje trajne obrasce – ali ključna pitanja ostaju","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/gut-bacteria-and-diet-a-10-000-person-study-with-l/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Velika studija pokazuje trajne obrasce – ali ključna pitanja ostaju"},"tags":["Microbiome","Nutrition","Public Health"],"geo":{"name":"Menlo Park, CA","lat":37.4529,"lon":-122.1817,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$a","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-how-neuron-groups-shape-memorywhat-we-know","title":"Kako skupine neurona grade sjećanja – što znamo?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Već više od stoljeća neurolozi i psiholozi pokušavaju razumjeti kako ljudski mozak podupire učenje i kodiranje sjećanja.","execSummary":"This article dissects the confirmed role of neuronal ensembles (engrams) in memory formation, emphasizing the gap between lab findings and clinical relevance. It critically assesses study limitations (sample sizes, animal models) and clarifies why this research doesn’t yet translate to patient care, while outlining its long-term potential for disorders like PTSD or Alzheimer’s.","keyPoints":["Više od stoljeća istraživanja pamćenja i učenja","Engrami: skupine neurona koje čuvaju usmjene","Ograničenja studija i što to znači za pacijente"],"source":{"name":"MedicalXpress","url":"https://medicalxpress.com/news/2026-03-groups-neurons-formation-memories.html"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/how-neuron-groups-shape-memorywhat-we-know/main.jpg","alt":"Kako skupine neurona grade sjećanja – što znamo?"},"subtitle":"Što studije stvarno pokazuju – i što još uvijek ne razumijemo","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/how-neuron-groups-shape-memorywhat-we-know/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što studije stvarno pokazuju – i što još uvijek ne razumijemo"},"tags":["Neuroplasticity","Memory Formation","Neural Networks"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$b","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-mrna-cancer-vaccines-what-we-know-what-we-don-t","title":"mRNA cjepiva protiv raka: što stvarno znamo, a što je nagađanje?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kad je riječ o liječenju raka, svaki korak naprijed nosi i teret očekivanja.","execSummary":"This article dissects the *actual* evidence behind mRNA cancer vaccines—separating confirmed lab progress from clinical reality. It highlights the gap between early-phase trials and patient accessibility, while addressing how misinformation risks distorting public perception of a technology that, despite promise, remains years from widespread use.","keyPoints":["Brzi napredak u razvoju mRNA cjepiva protiv tumora","Imunološki odgovor kao ključna meta, ali bez jasnog roka","Dezinformacije o mRNA tehnologiji još uvijek opterećuju javno mišljenje"],"source":{"name":"MedicalXpress","url":"https://medicalxpress.com/news/2026-03-cancer-vaccines-treatment-misinformation-mrna.html"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/mrna-cancer-vaccines-what-we-know-what-we-don-t/main.jpg","alt":"mRNA cjepiva protiv raka: što stvarno znamo, a što je nagađanje?"},"subtitle":"Nove studije donose nade, ali razlika između ‘obećavajućeg’ i ‘dokazanog’ ostaje ključna","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/mrna-cancer-vaccines-what-we-know-what-we-don-t/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Nove studije donose nade, ali razlika između ‘obećavajućeg’ i ‘dokazanog’ ostaje ključna"},"tags":["mRNA vaccines","oncology","cancer treatment"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$c","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-novartis-bets-3b-on-a-pi3k-inhibitorbut-how-solid-","title":"Novartis ulazi u onkologiju: 3 milijarde za Pikavation i SNV4818","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada farmaceutski div poput Novartisa uloži do 3 milijarde dolara u preuzimanje male biotehnološke tvrtke, to nije samo poslovni potez — to je signal o smjeru u kojem se kreće liječenje raka.","execSummary":"Novartis's $3B acquisition of Pikavation centers on SNV4818, an early-stage PI3Kα inhibitor for HR+/HER2- metastatic breast cancer. This analysis dissects the **evidence gap** between preliminary promise and clinical reality, emphasizing what the data *don’t* yet show for patients today. The move underscores industry trends in precision oncology but serves as a case study in how early-phase trials must be contextualized—lest hope outpace science.","keyPoints":["Novartis preuzima Pikavation za do 3 milijarde dolara","SNV4818 u ranoj kliničkoj fazi za HR+/HER2- metastatski rak dojke","Što ovo znači za pacijente danas — i što još uvijek ne znamo"],"source":{"name":"GEN News","url":"https://www.genengnews.com/topics/cancer/novartis-acquires-pikavation-for-up-to-3b-expanding-cancer-pipeline/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/novartis-bets-3b-on-a-pi3k-inhibitorbut-how-solid-/main.jpg","alt":"Novartis ulazi u onkologiju: 3 milijarde za Pikavation i SNV4818"},"subtitle":"Rana klinička ispitivanja, bez regulacijskog odobrenja","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/novartis-bets-3b-on-a-pi3k-inhibitorbut-how-solid-/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Rana klinička ispitivanja, bez regulacijskog odobrenja"},"tags":["Novartis","Oncology","Pikavation","SNV4818","Clinical Trials"],"geo":{"name":"Basel, Switzerland","lat":47.5577,"lon":7.5733,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$d","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-ozempics-mental-health-perks-real-or-research-mira","title":"Ozempic i mentalno zdravlje: što studija stvarno pokazuje?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada se lijek primarno namijenjen liječenju dijabetesa tipa 2 i kontroli težine – kao što je semaglutid (poznatiji pod trgovinskim imenom Ozempic) – poveže s poboljšanjem mentalnog zdravlja, medicinska zajednica pažljivo sluša.","execSummary":"A large observational study links Ozempic to reduced depression, anxiety, and addiction rates—but the mechanism remains unclear. This analysis dissects the evidence level, clinical irrelevance for current patients, and why regulatory bodies aren’t acting yet, framing it as a research signal rather than a therapeutic breakthrough.","keyPoints":["Smanjenje depresije i anksioznosti kod korisnika Ozempica","Manje psihijatrijskih hospitalizacija i ovisnosti za vrijeme terapije","Mehanizmi još uvijek nejasni – životni stil ili izravni učinak?"],"source":{"name":"ScienceDaily Health","url":"https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2026/03/260322020250.htm"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ozempics-mental-health-perks-real-or-research-mira/main.jpg","alt":"Ozempic i mentalno zdravlje: što studija stvarno pokazuje?"},"subtitle":"Velika studija otkriva neočekivane benefite, ali ostaju ključna pitanja o uzrocima i dugoročnim učincima","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/ozempics-mental-health-perks-real-or-research-mira/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Velika studija otkriva neočekivane benefite, ali ostaju ključna pitanja o uzrocima i dugoročnim učincima"},"tags":["Ozempic","Mental Health","Clinical Trial"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$e","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-roche-s-breast-cancer-pill-fails-key-first-line-tr","title":"Rocheov lijek za rak dojke ne uspijeva u ključnom ispitivanju","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada je Roche nedavno istaknuo kako njihov oralni lijek za rak dojke, persevERA, može postati najprodavaniji proizvod u povijesti tvrtke, očekivanja su bila visoka.","execSummary":"Roche’s breast cancer drug persevERA failed its pivotal Phase 3 trial, raising questions about its future and the gaps between early promise and clinical proof. This analysis dissects what the trial actually showed (and didn’t), the regulatory implications, and why this matters for precision oncology—without overstating the impact on current patient care.","keyPoints":["PersevERA ne ispunjava očekivanja u fazi 3","Potencijalni najprodavaniji lijek doživljava prepreku","Što ovo znači za pacijentice danas?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/roche-s-breast-cancer-pill-fails-key-first-line-tr/main.jpg","alt":"Rocheov lijek za rak dojke ne uspijeva u ključnom ispitivanju"},"subtitle":"Rezultati faze 3: što studija stvarno pokazuje i što ostaje nejasno","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/roche-s-breast-cancer-pill-fails-key-first-line-tr/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Rezultati faze 3: što studija stvarno pokazuje i što ostaje nejasno"},"tags":["Roche","Breast Cancer","Clinical Trial","Oncology"],"geo":{"name":"Basel, Switzerland","lat":47.5596,"lon":7.5886,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$f","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-ai-finds-no-brain-structure-link-to-navigation-ski","title":"Umjetna inteligencija ne pronalazi vezu između mozga i navigacije","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Desetljećima je znanstvena zajednica vjerovala da su izvanredne navigacijske vještine — poput brzog učenja složenih ruta — povezane s većim ili drugačije oblikovanim područjima mozga.","execSummary":"A University of Texas study using AI found no clear link between brain structure and navigation skills in young adults, challenging decades of assumptions—including famous London taxi driver research. The finding underscores the complexity of spatial cognition but offers no immediate clinical impact, instead pointing to gaps in how we measure brain-function relationships.","keyPoints":["AI alati nisu otkrili jasnu vezu strukture mozga i navigacijskih vještina","Studija iznosi u pitanje desetljeća pretpostavki o mozgovnoj plastičnosti","London taxi-vozači i dalje ključni primjer u istraživanjima navigacije"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ai-finds-no-brain-structure-link-to-navigation-ski/main.jpg","alt":"Umjetna inteligencija ne pronalazi vezu između mozga i navigacije"},"subtitle":"Što studija Stevena Weisberga stvarno pokazuje — i što ne","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/ai-finds-no-brain-structure-link-to-navigation-ski/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što studija Stevena Weisberga stvarno pokazuje — i što ne"},"tags":["Brain Navigation","Neuroscience","Steven Weisberg Study"],"geo":{"name":"Austin, Texas, United States","lat":30.2672,"lon":-97.7431,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$10","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-antibiotic-resistant-gbs-strains-may-explain-newbo","title":"Mutirani GBS sojevi: Zašto antibiotici ponekad ne štite novorođenčad?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Svake godine, tisuće novorođenčadi u svijetu obolijevaju od [Group B Streptococcus (GBS)](https://www.","execSummary":"The study identifies mutant GBS strains resistant to standard antibiotics, explaining persistent neonatal infections despite prophylaxis. While the findings highlight a gap in current protocols, they don’t change clinical practice yet—emphasizing the need for surveillance over alarm. The angle focuses on the tension between evolving bacterial threats and static prevention strategies.","keyPoints":["Mutacije omogućuju GBS preživljavanje u porodničkom kanalu","Antibiotici mogu biti manje učinkoviti protiv promijenjenih sojeva","Studija otvara pitanja o trenutnim preventivnim protokolima"],"source":{"name":"MedicalXpress","url":"https://medicalxpress.com/news/2026-03-mutant-group-strep-strains-infections.html"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/antibiotic-resistant-gbs-strains-may-explain-newbo/main.jpg","alt":"Mutirani GBS sojevi: Zašto antibiotici ponekad ne štite novorođenčad?"},"subtitle":"Novo istraživanje pokazuje kako evolucija bakterija izaziva nove rizike — ali što to znači za majke i bebe danas?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/antibiotic-resistant-gbs-strains-may-explain-newbo/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Novo istraživanje pokazuje kako evolucija bakterija izaziva nove rizike — ali što to znači za majke i bebe danas?"},"tags":["Group B Strep","Antibiotic Resistance","Neonatal Infection"],"geo":{"name":"East Lansing, United States","lat":42.7369,"lon":-84.4839,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$11","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-blood-marker-shows-promise-predicting-post-arrest-","title":"Novi krvni marker: rana prognoza kognitivnih oštećenja nakon srčanog zastoja?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Svake godine tisuće pacijenata preživljava izvanbolnički srčani zastoj, ali mnogi od njih kasnije suočavaju s trajnim kognitivnim oštećenjima koja značajno utječu na kvalitetu života.","execSummary":"A 2026 study presented at ESC Acute CardioVascular Care suggests that early measurement of neurofilament light chain (NfL) may improve prediction of cognitive impairment after out-of-hospital cardiac arrest. This analysis examines the evidence level (observational study), clinical relevance (none yet for patients), and critical gaps—including unknown sample size and methodology—while framing the finding as a research-stage signal rather than a practice-changing breakthrough.","keyPoints":["Neurofilament light chain kao potencijalni prediktor kognitivnih posljedica","Studija predstavljena na ESC Acute CardioVascular Care 2026","Rutinska mjerenja još uvijek nisu standard – što znače ovi rezultati?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/blood-marker-shows-promise-predicting-post-arrest-/main.jpg","alt":"Novi krvni marker: rana prognoza kognitivnih oštećenja nakon srčanog zastoja?"},"subtitle":"Što stvarno pokazuje nova studija o predviđanju kognitivnih oštećenja – i što još ne znamo","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/blood-marker-shows-promise-predicting-post-arrest-/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što stvarno pokazuje nova studija o predviđanju kognitivnih oštećenja – i što još ne znamo"},"tags":["Cardiac Arrest","Cognitive Impairment","Biomarker"],"geo":{"name":"Sophia Antipolis, France","lat":43.6053,"lon":7.0498,"countryCode":"FR"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$12","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-how-cholesterol-fuels-prostate-cancerand-why-it-ma","title":"FGFR1 i rak prostate: zašto masnoća u stanicama mijenja tijek bolesti?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada se u stanicama raka prostate nakuplja kolesterol, tumor može postati agresivniji i otporniji na liječenje.","execSummary":"The study identifies FGFR1 as a key regulator of cholesterol uptake in prostate cancer cells, potentially explaining tumor progression and treatment resistance. However, the research remains preclinical—no patient impact yet. The angle focuses on separating confirmed lab findings from speculative clinical implications, emphasizing methodology limits and the long road to therapeutic relevance.","keyPoints":["FGFR1 povećava unos kolesterola u stanicama raka prostate","Mehanizam može objasniti otpornost tumora na terapiju","Za pacijente danas — još uvijek samo laboratorijski nalaz"],"source":{"name":"MedicalXpress","url":"https://medicalxpress.com/news/2026-03-fgfr1-boosts-cholesterol-uptake-prostate.html"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/how-cholesterol-fuels-prostate-cancerand-why-it-ma/main.jpg","alt":"FGFR1 i rak prostate: zašto masnoća u stanicama mijenja tijek bolesti?"},"subtitle":"Što studija s Teksaškog sveučilišta stvarno pokazuje — i što ostaje nejasno","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/how-cholesterol-fuels-prostate-cancerand-why-it-ma/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što studija s Teksaškog sveučilišta stvarno pokazuje — i što ostaje nejasno"},"tags":["Prostate Cancer","FGFR1","Cancer Research"],"geo":{"name":"College Station, United States","lat":30.627977,"lon":-96.334407,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$13","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-153-studies-link-youth-screen-time-to-mental-healt","title":"Ekrani i mentalno zdravlje: što 153 studije stvarno kažu?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Ako vaše dijete provodi sate pred ekranom, jesu li to samo „suvremena djeca“ – ili razlog za zabrinutost.","execSummary":"This analysis cuts through the hype around a major JAMA Pediatrics review linking youth screen time to later mental health risks, emphasizing what the observational data *actually* show (correlations, not causation) and why clinicians should treat the findings as a research priority—not a clinical directive. The angle focuses on the gap between evidence and actionable guidance, framing it as a call for more rigorous study designs.","keyPoints":["Veća upotreba digitalnih medija povezuje se s kasnijim teškoćama","Analiza prati djecu do 20 godina – ali ne dokazuje uzročnost","Što roditelji i pedijatri mogu učiniti s ovim podacima?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/153-studies-link-youth-screen-time-to-mental-healt/main.jpg","alt":"Ekrani i mentalno zdravlje: što 153 studije stvarno kažu?"},"subtitle":"Najopsežniji pregled do sada otkriva korelacije, ali ostavlja ključna pitanja otvorenima","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/153-studies-link-youth-screen-time-to-mental-healt/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Najopsežniji pregled do sada otkriva korelacije, ali ostavlja ključna pitanja otvorenima"},"tags":["Mental Health","Screen Time","Correlation Studies"],"geo":{"name":"Townsville, Australia","lat":-19.259028,"lon":146.816943,"countryCode":"AU"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$14","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-new-dopamine-signal-found-in-mouse-brain-study","title":"Dopaminski signal: mozak nas usmjerava prema cilju?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada naš mozak odlučuje jesmo li na pravom putu prema nekom cilju, možda nam u tome pomaže dotad nepoznati signal dopamina.","execSummary":"This study identifies a dopamine signal linked to goal-directed movement in mice, offering insights into how the brain processes visual cues—but its relevance to human medicine remains speculative. The angle focuses on separating confirmed findings from overreach, emphasizing study limits (animal model, controlled settings) and the absence of clinical applications today.","keyPoints":["Novi dopaminski signal povezan s kretanjem prema cilju","Studija na miševima objavljena u *Nature* – razina dokaza?","Što ovo znači za razumijevanje vizualne obrade u ljudskom mozgu?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/new-dopamine-signal-found-in-mouse-brain-study/main.jpg","alt":"Dopaminski signal: mozak nas usmjerava prema cilju?"},"subtitle":"Što studija stvarno pokazuje – i što još uvijek ne znamo","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/new-dopamine-signal-found-in-mouse-brain-study/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što studija stvarno pokazuje – i što još uvijek ne znamo"},"tags":["Dopamine Signaling","Neuroscience","Brain Function"],"geo":{"name":"Boston, United States","lat":42.3601,"lon":-71.0589,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$15","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-19-in-vivo-car-t-cell-breakthroughbut-how-far-from-pa","title":"Dvovektorski sustav stvara CAR-T stanice izravno u tijelu","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-19T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-19T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Imunoterapija CAR-T stanicama već desetljećima mijenja liječenje određenih vrsta raka, ali je njen najveći nedostatak u tome što zahtijeva složeno i skupo *ex vivo* modificiranje pacijentovih stanica.","execSummary":"This article dissects a new two-vector system for in vivo CAR-T cell generation, framing its preclinical success (leukemia, myeloma, solid tumor) against the reality of clinical translation. The angle focuses on the gap between promising lab results and patient impact, emphasizing regulatory hurdles, scalability questions, and the 10+ year timeline typical for such therapies.","keyPoints":["Dvovektorska strategija generira CAR-T stanice *in vivo*","Preklinički modeli pokazali djelotvornost kod tri vrste raka","Još uvijek daleko od kliničke primjene na ljudima"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/in-vivo-car-t-cell-breakthroughbut-how-far-from-pa/main.jpg","alt":"Dvovektorski sustav stvara CAR-T stanice izravno u tijelu"},"subtitle":"Što studija stvarno pokazuje – i što još moramo saznati","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/in-vivo-car-t-cell-breakthroughbut-how-far-from-pa/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što studija stvarno pokazuje – i što još moramo saznati"},"tags":["CAR-T cells","gene therapy","immunotherapy"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$16","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-17-a-new-tool-for-secretory-antibodiesbut-will-it-sca","title":"Nova kromatografska metoda za pročišćavanje antitijela: što znači?","category":"medicine","date":"2026-03-17T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-17T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Sekretorno immunoglobulin A (IgA) već desetljećima privlači pažnju imunologa zbog svoje uloge u zaštiti sluznica – od dišnih puteva do crijevnog trakta.","execSummary":"Austrian researchers developed a chromatography method for secretory IgA purification, targeting large-scale therapy production—but the study remains preclinical with no patient data. This analysis dissects the gap between lab promise and clinical reality, emphasizing unresolved questions about scalability, cost, and regulatory hurdles that determine whether this will ever reach patients.","keyPoints":["Austrijski znanstvenici razvili metodu za sekretorno IgA antitijela","Potencijal za industrijsku proizvodnju terapija – ali još bez kliničkih dokaza","Tehnika još nije testirana u pacijenata ni odobrena od regulatora"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/a-new-tool-for-secretory-antibodiesbut-will-it-sca/main.jpg","alt":"Nova kromatografska metoda za pročišćavanje antitijela: što znači?"},"subtitle":"Korak naprijed u laboratoriju – ali koliko je blizu bolesničkog kreveta?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/a-new-tool-for-secretory-antibodiesbut-will-it-sca/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Korak naprijed u laboratoriju – ali koliko je blizu bolesničko